Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're talking about serenity.\NSerenity that uh arises then as an
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:01:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,automatic consequence of understanding\Nand comprehension. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nit's uh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,affirmative, simplistic, non-operative\Nand people it's invitational.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Invitational. No promotion. No\Npromotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nonpredictive because reality is\Nnonlinear. You cannot tell what the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,secret is. Now why can why would that\Nbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it you can't tell the future?\N>> There'd be no point to existence, human
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,existence. Why? Because the future then\Nis created by every choice and every
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,option you make. Is it not? Every choice\Nand option determines where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,within the overall infinite field.\NBecause the future hasn't happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no reality. And you can't\Nyou can't calibrate the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,anything that is not a reality. You\Nknow, is a fiction. So there's fictional
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,propositions about the future.\NBut the future obviously is not a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,possibility or there would be no point\Nto creation, no point to divinity or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,existence, much less human life.\NUhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying? It's\Nonly by because you have an option. You
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,could choose this or that. Well, if this\Nthe outcome was determined, there'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no point to human life, would there?\NWe'd all be in some other realm where
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you're done already.\NAnd if you blew it, you blew it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you blew it, boy, you blew it. Okay?\NIt's not sentimental. We said you know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the value of being empathic.\NI know what it is to walk in my
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,brother's mocca sense. That's empathy.\NThat's coming from the heart of humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,within you. Your heart understands where\Ntheir heart is. So I understand how they
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,feel. Sympathy is joining them which is\Nsomething else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As a psychiatrist you're empathic but\Nyou won't last long if you're
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sympathetic. sympathetic.\NYeah. So the amateur offers sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which is a way of seduction. Sympathy is\Na form of seduction and exploitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Empathy allows you both to remaintain\Nyour own integrity. I understand how you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,feel. Non-scentimentals,\Nnon-authoritarian,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no rules. Teachers are respected but\Ndon't walk around with special titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Neducational
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,provides information. So it's p\Nprimarily educative and inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's self-supporting. It's freestanding\Ndevoid of induced or altered states of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. Uh which is something\Nelse I just got through writing about.
