Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears. State disappears.\NA prevailing level of consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not dependent on externals much less\Nphysical physicality or physical
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,manipulations.\NWe said that
