Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,are the automatic consequence of that\Nwhich you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So to take classes on learning how to\Nfly or billocate or
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,anything like that\Nyou can see
