Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,really go nuts. All right. Uh, we'll\Nmove past that one. All right. We want
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the dualities of attraction\Nand aversion. Uh because these apply to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,all the levels of consciousness. All the\Nlevels of consciousness are held in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,place by what I call is the ego juice of\Nthe payoff. You're getting a payoff and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you look at letting go of it in a\Nnegative way. So you develop an
