Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,often have we heard that? I can forgive\Nhim, but he doesn't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive him, but he doesn't deserve\Nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard all the veterans of World War II\Nlong ago go forgiven their enemy uh the
