Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the girls ranch every month. He had his\Nlicense places. Kiss me, I'm Polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, you love all the Polish\Npeople and you really always feel like
