Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,course is much weaker. And in, you know,\Nkarate and various martial arts, um, and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,various other things I've done, uh, you\Ntry to provoke the guy to get mad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because once he's get mad, you've got\Nhim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You got him. You got him. The minute you\Ngot him mad, he freezes into an angry
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, space.\NInstantly, you got him. In a flash, the
