Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,just goes to work and goes to church on\NSunday. I mean, what's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I want to meditate and think\Nabout nothing? You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the ego loves excitement and hates\Nserenity. Sees it as boredom.
